snippet.title: Equestria at War 2022 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Equestria Global News Presents:

As the ports of Zebrica open for travel, come take a look at the world of Equestria at War. This video was made to showcase several interesting parts of the mod, both old and new.

Enjoy!

www.equestriaatwar.com

Join us on Discord: https://discord.com/invite/kPkNFb5
Steam page: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1826643372

Special thanks to: Podrick Equus (Editor), RedSpark(Composer) and the EaW Artist Team 

1st song by iamnotacleverpony: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yhC5SLS4j5o 

2nd song by RedSpark: https://youtu.be/iEkqUzW89wk

Equestria at War is a fan-made modification for Hearts of Iron IV, not related or endorsed by Paradox Interactive or Hasbro.
